============================
- Carregar módulo do Swift -
============================

> module load swift/0.96.2 

============================
- Configurações ------------
============================

> export SWIFT_USERHOME=$SCRATCH

============================
- Tutorial -----------------
============================
TODO: Colocar swift.conf nos diretórios 

-- Copiar diretório tutorial do swift para o SCRATCH

> cd tutorial 
> source setup.sh

= 0. Hello Swift ==========

> cd hello
> swift hello.swift

> swiftlog -import-provenance <run_id>

> cd ..

= 1. Part01 ==========

> cd part01
> swift p1.swift
> cat sim.out

> swiftlog -import-provenance <run_id>

> cd ..

= 2. Part02 ==========

> cd part02
> swift p1.swift
> ls -ltrh output
> cat output/sim_1.out

> swiftlog -import-provenance <run_id>

> cd ..

= 3. Part03 ==========

> cd part03
> swift p3.swift
> ls -ltrh output
> more output/*out

> swiftlog -import-provenance <run_id>

> cd ..

= 4. Part04 ==========

> cd part04
> swift p4.swift
> ls -ltrh output
> more output/sim_1.log

> swiftlog -import-provenance <run_id>

> cd ..

= 5. Part05 ==========

> cd part05
> swift p5.swift
> ls -ltrh output
> more output/average*

> swiftlog -import-provenance <run_id>

> cd ..

= 6. Part06 ==========

> cd part06
> swift p6.swift
> ls -ltrh output
> more output/average*

> swiftlog -import-provenance <run_id>

> cd ..

